&lt;li data-start=&quot;2653&quot; data-end=&quot;2720&quot;&gt;A consistent track record of meeting or exceeding revenue targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2723&quot; data-end=&quot;2814&quot;&gt;Experience running complex, consultative sales cycles with technical or analytical buyers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2817&quot; data-end=&quot;2880&quot;&gt;Strong discovery, storytelling, and objection-handling skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2883&quot; data-end=&quot;2949&quot;&gt;Comfort operating in ambiguity and rapidly evolving environments&lt;/li&gt;
