&lt;li&gt;Drive account growth through upsells, renewals, and referrals by ensuring customers succeed with Baselayer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become an expert in customers&#39; workflows and pain points - then work with internal teams to address them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop playbooks, feedback loops, and operational processes that help scale the AM/CS function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly to the CEO and collaborate with product and engineering on scaling customer operations&amp;nbsp;🤝&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
