&lt;li&gt;Link individuals to businesses via public web evidence (e.g. confirming a named officer or employee genuinely works there).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop risk/legitimacy scoring derived from web-presence signals, fed back into downstream underwriting.&lt

