&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;As Baselayer&#39;s first dedicated Sr. Product Manager, you&#39;ll report directly to our GM, Agentic Economy and own the creation, design, and full scoping of new products that take Baselayer beyond financial institutions and into new verticals where business identity is broken. You&#39;ll define what we build, why we build it, and what &quot;done&quot; looks like. You won&#39;t be inheriting a roadmap. You&#39;ll be writing one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;This role is hands-on. You&#39;ll write the specs, draw the wireframes, partner with design, and sit in eng standups. You&#39;ll also own the existing product surface: setting priorities, sequencing the roadmap, and making the daily calls that keep engineering shipping the right things. New verticals are the headline, but the day-to-day is a mix of zero-to-one product definition and disciplined operating cadence on what&#39;s already in market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot; data-start=&quot;1226&quot; data-end=&quot;1244&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;12

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT BASELAYER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every day, financial institutions make consequential decisions about which businesses to onboard and trust, in order to grow with confidence. Baselayer exists to make those decisions faster, more accurate, and much less expensive. We offer the leading AI Risk Platform that automates merchant onboarding, underwriting, and fraud prevention for over 20% of the Financial Institutions in America. By combining authoritative government data, AI agents purpose-built for web analysis, and a network powered by millions of applications, Baselayer prevents billions of dollars in merchant fraud and credit risk and instantly automates good merchant applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE TEAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a small team solving a big problem. Business fraud costs the financial system billions every year, and the tools built to fight it are slow, expensive, and outdated. We&#39;re changing that. You&#39;d be joining a small, close-knit team where ownership is real, customer impact is immediate, and the work you ship matters from day one. We move deliberately, communicate directly, and care deeply about quality. If you want to look back in five years and know you worked on something that changed how trust works across major financial institutions, let&#39;s chat!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot; data-start=&quot;718&quot; data-end=&quot;1002&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;718&quot; data-end=&quot;736&quot;&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baselayer is growing, and we&#39;re looking for a Technical Recruiter to help us hire the people who will define the company. You&#39;ll be owning full-cycle talent acquisition across Engineering, Product, and Design roles. This is a high-impact, high-ownership role — you&#39;ll work directly with founders and hiring managers to build a bar-raising hiring process and bring exceptional people into the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own full-cycle recruiting for roles across Engineering, Product and Design — from sourcing through offer close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with founders and hiring managers to define role requirements, build scorecards, and maintain a high hiring bar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage sourcing strategies to proactively identify top talent through LinkedIn, referrals, events, and creative outreach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage candidate experience end-to-end, ensuring every candidate has a respectful, clear, and timely process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and improve our ATS, keeping pipelines clean and data accurate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and iterate on interview processes that are structured, fair, and predictive of on-the-job success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to employer brand efforts — help tell the Baselayer story to attract candidates who are excited about our mission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track recruiting metrics and report on pipeline health, time-to-fill, and quality of hire&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of full-cycle recruiting experience, ideally at a high-growth startup or in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success hiring across Engineering and/or Product roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sourcing skills — you know how to find and engage passive candidates, not just manage inbound&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and organizational skills; you run a tight, candidate-friendly process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with an ATS (Greenhouse, Lever, Ashby, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with LinkedIn Recruiter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
